    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "Title",
      "text": "How to fold the world’s best paper airplane"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "NarrativeText",
      "text": "In 2012, Joe Ayoob broke the world record for the longest distance paper airplane flight with a plane designed by John Collins. In this video, Collins demonstrates how to fold that plane, the Suzanne.",
      "metadata": {
        "parent_id": "984d9b09a3b5dd0c7219fae738f39a19"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "Text",
      "text": "Directions for the design are also available in Collins’ New World Champion Paper Airplane Book.",
      "metadata": {
        "parent_id": "984d9b09a3b5dd0c7219fae738f39a19"
      }
